---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";

import Container from "../components/ui/Container.astro";
---

<MainLayout

title="AI Solutions by Industry | Ragan Dynamics"

description="Practical AI consulting and automation solutions for Singapore SMEs across multiple industries."

>


<section class="bg-slate-50 py-20">


<Container>


<div class="text-center">


<h1 class="text-5xl font-black text-slate-900">

AI Solutions Across Industries

</h1>


<p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-3xl text-xl text-slate-600">

We help Singapore SMEs adopt practical AI solutions
that improve productivity, reduce costs and accelerate growth.

</p>


</div>




<div class="mt-16 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">



<!-- Professional Services -->

<div class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-sm">


<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">

Professional Services

</h2>


<p class="mt-4 text-slate-600">

AI assistants, document automation,
knowledge management and workflow optimisation.

</p>


</div>




<!-- Retail -->

<div class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-sm">


<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">

Retail & E-Commerce

</h2>


<p class="mt-4 text-slate-600">

Customer support automation,
personalisation and sales insights.

</p>


</div>




<!-- Manufacturing -->

<div class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-sm">


<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">

Manufacturing

</h2>


<p class="mt-4 text-slate-600">

AI-driven operations,
predictive insights and process improvement.

</p>


</div>




<!-- Healthcare -->

<div class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-sm">


<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">

Healthcare

</h2>


<p class="mt-4 text-slate-600">

Secure AI solutions for administration,
documentation and efficiency.

</p>


</div>




<!-- Finance -->

<div class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-sm">


<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">

Finance & Accounting

</h2>


<p class="mt-4 text-slate-600">

Automate reporting,
analysis and repetitive workflows.

</p>


</div>




<!-- SMEs -->

<div class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 shadow-sm">


<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">

Small & Medium Enterprises

</h2>


<p class="mt-4 text-slate-600">

Affordable AI adoption strategies
designed for SME budgets.

</p>


</div>


</div>



<div class="mt-16 rounded-3xl bg-slate-900 p-10 text-center">


<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">

Ready to explore AI for your industry?

</h2>


<a

href="/contact"

class="mt-8 inline-flex rounded-xl bg-blue-600 px-8 py-4 font-bold text-white hover:bg-blue-700"

>

Talk to an AI Consultant

</a>


</div>



</Container>


</section>


</MainLayout>